<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include("head.ejs", { title }) %>
  <body>
    <%- include("navbar.ejs") %>

    <style>
      .signin-btn {
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        margin-top: 40px;
        width: 380px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 400;
        font-family: "Sen", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue",
          sans-serif;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        line-height: 2rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 2px;
        color: #333;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        box-shadow: 0px 7px 0px 0px #9a9a9a;
        -webkit-box-shadow: 0px 7px 0px 0px #9a9a9a;
        -moz-box-shadow: 0px 7px 0px 0px #9a9a9a;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
      }

      .signin-btn:focus {
        transform: translateY(7px);
        box-shadow: none;
      }

      .signin-btn img {
        height: 2rem;
        width: auto;
        margin-right: 10px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      ul {
        margin-top: 30px;
        max-width: 500px;
        list-style-type: none;
      }

      ul li {
        margin: 10px 0;
        text-align: justify;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 450px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 1.4rem;
        }

        .signin-btn img {
          height: 1.5rem;
        }

        .signin-btn {
          line-height: 1.5rem;
					font-size: 0.8rem;
					width: 280px;
        }
      }
      @media screen and (max-width: 350px) {
        h1 {
          font-size: 1.3rem;
        }
      }
    </style>

    <div class="body-container">
      <div class="flex-container">
        <div>
          <div>
            <h1 style="text-align: center;">Instructions</h1>
            <ul>
              <li>
                The hunt shall commence on 2:00 PM 21st August 2020 and will
                continue till 8:00 PM 22nd August 2020.
              </li>
              <li>
                All participants are recommended to read the
                <a
                  href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1bpeRtE2YC09lHyKIuPUFJkxxp1gfuPPvRneCMJxPv7U/edit"
                  >Cryptic Hunt resources</a
                >
              </li>
              <li>
                The event encompasses an Online Cryptic Treasure Hunt in which
                participants must make their way through a series of cryptic
                levels.
              </li>
              <li>
                The participant's aim is to crack the levels as quickly as they
                can so as to place themselves at the top of the leaderboard.
              </li>
              <li>
                At each level, the participants will encounter a number of clues
                which shall all, together, point to one answer. Each level has
                one correct answer.
              </li>
              <li>
                Official clues may be released on our Facebook Page if and when
                deemed necessary by the admins.
              </li>
              <li>
                Lead confirmations will be done via the Facebook page itself.
              </li>
              <li>
                Answers will always be lower-case, alphanumeric and will contain
                no spaces. Special characters are allowed. For example, if the
                answer is Big Bang, you would type it in as “bigbang”.
              </li>
              <li>
                Every clue in the question is important. If it wasn't important,
                it wouldn't be there.
              </li>
              <li>Beware of the spelling you enter, we do not auto correct.</li>
              <li>
                And if it was not obvious, team play, answer sharing, hint
                sharing and collaborating with other competitors in general is
                not allowed and any such evidence can lead to disqualification.
              </li>
              <li>
                You can come back to this page any time by clicking on the
                Sudocrypt logo in the top left corner of the page.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <% if(!authenticated) { %>
          <div style="margin: 40px 0;">
            <h1 style="text-align: center;">Sign in to start playing</h1>
            <a href="/auth/google" class="signin-btn">
              <img src="/dpsrkp192.png" alt="DPSRKP" />
              Sign in with @dpsrkp.net</a
            >
          </div>
          <% }%>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("footer.ejs") %>
  </body>
</html>
